2. Set up Stripe secrets in Firebase
firebase functions:secrets:set STRIPE_SECRET_KEY
# Enter your Stripe secret key (starts with sk_)

firebase functions:secrets:set STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET
# Enter your webhook signing secret (you'll get this after step 4)
3. Deploy Cloud Functions
firebase deploy --only functions

4. Configure Stripe Webhook
In your Stripe Dashboard:
Go to Developers â†’ Webhooks
Add endpoint: https://us-central1-halifaxpickuphockey-50910.cloudfunctions.net/stripeWebhook
Select event: checkout.session.completed
Copy the signing secret and set it using the command in step 2

5. Test with Stripe test mode
Use test card: 4242 4242 4242 4242 with any future date and CVC



